Package: ReducedHeat
Title: Produces heatmap from a 1d dimensional reduction
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Miles",
           family = "Smith",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "miles-smith@omrf.org")
Description: Inspired by (and borrowing code from) \link[=https://github.com/KlugerLab/t-SNE-Heatmaps]{t-SNE-Heatmaps} from the Kluger Lab, this allows one to examine gene expression patterns along a 1d projection of a reduced dimension (i.e. tSNE, UMAP, etc...)
